queries.name: Columbus - Count
queries.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as value FROM dbo.oe_hdr WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE location_id = '01' AND completed = 'N'

queries.name: Columbus - Count (Alt)
queries.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as value FROM dbo.oe_hdr WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE location_id = '1' AND completed = 'N'

queries.name: Columbus - Sales
queries.query: SELECT ISNULL(SUM(l.extended_price), 0) as value FROM dbo.oe_hdr h WITH (NOLOCK) JOIN dbo.oe_line l WITH (NOLOCK) ON h.order_no = l.order_no WHERE h.location_id = '01' AND h.order_date >= DATEADD(day, -30, GETDATE())

queries.name: Columbus - Sales (Alt)
queries.query: SELECT ISNULL(SUM(l.extended_price), 0) as value FROM dbo.oe_hdr h WITH (NOLOCK) JOIN dbo.oe_line l WITH (NOLOCK) ON h.order_no = l.order_no WHERE h.location_id = '1' AND h.order_date >= DATEADD(day, -30, GETDATE())
